'Bhortonattyom'' ho ek obhizat bharti-i nachacho prokar. Tachea namvauyleanuch bhortachea nattyoxastrakodden sombond axil'leachem spoxtt zata. Bhortonattyom' hi ek som'mixr kola. Tichebhitor kauy, natty, songit, tal ani loi hea soglleancho aspavo zata. Nortikechea hatapamyanchi halchal, sonketik va sadrixyodrxok hatacheo mudra, tal, loi ani kauy him sogllim bhortonattyomachim bhavo uktaupachim sadhnam. Hea sogllea angantlean khoincho tori divy oso sondex prekxokam'meren pavoup ani prekxokank tanche vastou ovsthentolean titlea kallameren tori voilea pamvddeacher vhorop oso hea nachacho het asta. Nachantole kothaprosong ramainn, mohabharot,purannam ani mohakaveam hatuntlean ghetil'le astat. Tea tea prosongantole te te vyoktichem onukoronn kolakar korit asta. Bhortonattyomachi sadhna ho ek yog oxem mhonnttat. Hea nachant mudra ani dolleamni uloupachem asta. Tekhatir sadhkak kaim nem' ani potheam pallchim poddttat. Purannant ani agmant (xastr) xiv ho zoso nortok toxench to yogi-i asa. Nottraz hi tachi nrityokolentoli upadhi.
Bhortonattyom'

Bhortonattyom' hi ek don hozar vorsamsaun prochlit asa. Bhortonattyom' hi xoili mull tomillonadduntlea tonzaur jilheachi mhonnun namna asa. Ho nach chodd korun bailoch kortat. I. So. Dus-ya - tis-ya xenkddeantolea 'xilppodhikarom'' hea tomill gronthat hea nachacho ul'lekh melltta. Tonzaurchea chol razanche karkirdint hea nachachi pod'dot axil'li. Tancheuporant naik raje hamnni hea nachak khub urba dili. 18 vea xenkddeant tonzaurak protaposimh ani tache uprant tullzaji hanchea kallant he kolechi khub udrogot zali. Tanchea dorbarantole rajkovi mohadevo onn'nnavi ho nattyoxastrantolo vidvan ani subborai hedd ut'tom' nortok mhonnun gajle. Subboroyache char put chin'noyea, pon'noyea, voddivelu ani xivnondom' hea pill'lle bhavancho 'orengettrom'' (poilo rongmachoyer provex),dusro sorfoji moharaz (kar. 1798-1832) hachea dorbarant 1825 vorsa zalo. Hea charui bhavank aichea poromporagot bhortonattyom' pod'dotiche ad'd prourtok mantat. Hea charui bhavamni telugunt kaim tomill bhaxent rochil'le nachache prokar poromporagot nrityopd'dot mhonnun ruddh zaleat. Hech sodeachea bhortonattyomache prokar asat.

Survek hea nrityoprokarak 'kut'tu', 'att'ttom'' oxim namva axil'lim. Uprant deudasimni hea nriteachi zotnai gheun zopasona keli. Tokhatir taka 'dasiatt'ttom'' hea namvan vollkhunk lagle asumye. Punn dusro sorfoji bhomsle hannem aple sodrent va dorbarant ho nach korpachi porompora chalik laun hea nachak prochixttha melloun dili. Ten'nasaun hea nachak 'sodoratt'ttom'' mhollear dorbari nach hi manachi suvat favo zali. Telugu sahiteant nrityonatteacho 'bhortoxastr' oso ul'lekh melltta. Bhavo, rag ani tal hancho zannkar to bhorot oxem bhortoxastrant manil'lean sodoratt'ttom' nachakuch uprant bhortonattyom' mhonnunk lagle.

Hea nachachea odheaponachi survat bo-ya mhurtacher vidhiyukt pujen kortat. Survek xikoitat tea podaghatank 'oddvu' oxem mhonnttat. Oddvu mhollear nachpachi survechi halchal. Hea pamyanche halchalink tomill-telugu bhaxent oddu va oddvu oxem mhonnttat. Hea oddvunche khaxele pongodd asat te oxe-

