2) olaripu ho bhortonattyomantolo poilo prokar. Purvil'lea gronthamni hacho 'puxpanzoli' oso ul'lekh melltta. Puxpanzoli mhollear fulancho poso. Nortoki rongmachoyer yetkochothoim axil'lea sogllea deutank puxpanzoli omppacho ho prokar. Komoll jepromann lhou lhou paklle-pakllen fulta techpromann hi nortoki aple dolle, man, bhumveo, khande hanchea nazuk halchalimni survat korta. Hea halchalimni eke torecho veayam' zal'lean nachacheo fuddleo halchali chopllayen korunk mellttat. Hea prokarocho dusro het oso, nortoki apleamatheacher tonddasamokar ani hodd'ddeacher onjli hosot dourun vighnohrta, rongdeuta, guru ani vidvanank nomskar korta ani fuddli kareavoll yoxsvi zaupakhatir axirvad nomskar magta. Tot, toi, toiyum', tam' hea kar vachok bolanchi hi rochna asta. He bol ragdarint mhollear purvil'lea xastri-i gronthapromann 'nottoi' va natt rangant gaitat. Olaripu chotuxradi vingodd vingodd zatimni kortat.

3) zotisvor mho bhortonattyomantolo dusro prokar. Zoti mhollear bol ani svorom' mhollear svor. Kotthinn oxa hea nrityoprokarant man, hat ani pam-i hancheo talobd'd halchali astat. Rag, svor ani tal hanchea somyogan ho prokar akrxok korpacho asta. Ho xudhd nach axil'lean nrity hea prokarant moddtta. Hem nrity chalu astona vadeancher khoinchyai tori ragachi dhun vazoitat.

4) xobdom' devadikanchea nattyopurnn kothaprosongancher adarit kauy mhollear xobdom'. Somskritant haka yoxogiti oxem mhonnttat. Hea gitant devachi va konnai naikachi tokhnnai asta. 'salmure' mhollear tumkam nomskar kortam hea utran hea gitacho xeutt zata. Hea nriteant mudrancho upeg kortat. Bhavo ani mudra hanchea adaran hatunt gitacho orth uktaitat. Kounak sobsaroke addavo nachpachi hatunt yeuzonn asta.

5) vornnom' vornnom' mhollear bhortonattyomacho gabhoch. Haka 'podournn' va 'choukournn' oxam-i nava asat. Ho nrityoprokar samko guspagondollacho ani kotthinn asta. Nrity, songit ani obhinoi hancho kolapurnn somyog mhollear vornnom'. Nortokachem budhdikouxly ani obhinoikouxly hatunt chodd dixtti poddtta. Hatunt gey podeacho orth zos-zoso bodlota. Hostomudramni koulacho orth ani mukragan tatuntlea ontorbhaunecheo vingodd vingodd chhotta dakhoupacheo astat. Rag, tal, ani bhavo hancho trivenni songom' sadun obhinoyachim vegvegollim angam dakhoupachim axil'lean ho nach purai zaupak ek vor tori lagta. Vilombit, modhy ani drut oxo tinuy loyi hea nriteakhatir vaprotat.

6) podom' vornnomantlea halchalink lagun nortoki thokta, tekhatir tika suxegachi goroz asta. Dekhun podom' ho vegllo pod'doticho nach kortat. Hatunt mudra-obhinoyacher bhor divn soukasayen nachtat. Podom' mhollear premgit. Tatunt pol'lovi, onupl'lovi ani choronn oso krom' asta. Devo, raza hancher him podam rochil'lim astat. Hatuntolim choddxim podam tixr-triputt talant gaitat. 'mixrom'', 'mixr chapu' va fokot 'chapu' him sogllim tixr zati-triputt talachinch namvam asat. Him podam vilombit loyent gaupachi chal asa.

8) zaulli ho chodd korun modhy loyint uddtte chalint gaupacho prokar. Hatuntolem sahity xringaros prodhan asta. Nayika va tichi ixttinn zaullintlean aple bhauvikar uktaita. Hatuntlea xringarobhavachem svorup ekekodam sadem-sompem, loukik ani kaim fauttim ut'tan asta. Hanchi pol'livi, onupl'lovi ani choronn oxi rochna asta. Ken'naken'nai ekaporos chodd legit choronn astat.

9) til'lana til'lana mhollear hindusthani songitantolo toranna. Hatunt 'til'lilana' ,dirna' 'tom' dirna', 'ton'nom'' oslea prokaranche bol ekttham-i korun tanchi ragant ani talant boska kel'li asta. Hatunt goti, zox ani vegvegolle podaghat astat. Tatuntole svor, loi ani bol khaxelem vatauronn toyar kortat. Hatunt loikarik chodd mhotv asun nortikechea angachem vegvegllea konxamni ani xorirausthantolean dorxon ghoddoita. Songit ho hea karyokromancho atmo asta.

10) virut'tom' churnnika ani xrlok tinuy prokar ekamekank samke lagim asun te tomill telugu ani somskrit bhaxantlean sador kortat.

11) koutukmy linchea kallant ho prokar fokot deullamninch polloupak mellttalo, punn halim ho prokar rongmachoyer olaripu poilim kortat. Purvil'lea gronthamni hacho ul'lekh 'kout', 'kut't' oso melltta. Hatuntlea bolancher yogy tem nrity ani sahiteacher obhinoi kortat.

12) mongllom' proyogachea xeuttak gaupacho ho prokar. Hacher nach korinat, punn nortoki fokot podaghat korta. Proyogant zal'lea git, vady, nrity hatuntlea chukamvixim devakodden chuk magop, ho hea mongllom' prokaracho mukhel het asta. Mongllom' mhollear 'sogllem mongoll zaum, borem zaum' oxi devak kel'li prarthona. Hoch proyogacho xeutt asta.

==Bhes==

Poilinchea kallant bhortonattyom' nachakhatir nortoki sodlloso chuddidar ani paizomo vaprotali. Tacher erogenddi kopddoyachi nnou vari dhoviful'l saddi dhomprasokoil meren nhemsun davea khandauylean podor gheun to ujve kuxikoddlean fuddem haddun dave votten komrak khoitalim. He saddyek pavo inch rundayechi bhangra korachi zor astali. Dekhun he saddyek 'tuya seloi' oxem mhonnttale. Ticher komrak 'maza' cho komropotto ani voir rongit blauz ghalun soglle olonkar ghaltalim. Punn halim hea bhesant khub suttsuttitoponna ailam. Choleank nnou vari saddi nhespak zodd zata mhonnun, toxech torecho bhes ximvun toyar kortat. Ho bhes xalvacho ximvtat. Pum' ho bhes kas ghalun nhexil'lea pitambora bhaxen asun taka donuy vottamni ximvil'lo dhomprameren paupi ponkho asta. Tacher komrak gutthlail'lo teach kopddeacho xelo asta ani tea xeleakuy bomble sokoil yeta oso ek lhanso ponkho asta. Her olonkar mat poromporik pod'dotipromann astat. Mhollear golleant gollobhor mallo, hatbhor kanknnam, koplar bhangtillo, bazubond, nakant toxench nakache modim lambto 'bulak' namvacho olonkar ani pamyant bhorpur ghungur bandtat.

Poilinchea kallant ho nach choddso deullamni toxench lognasarokilea mongol suvalleamni korop zatalo. Punn uprant to rajdorobarant ani halim veusayik rongmachoyer toxench her somskritik kareavollimni pollounk melltta.

Bhortonattyomachea proyogant mridong, vinna, vayolin, murli, zhanz, chiplleo oxa vadeanchi sath asta. Tistr, choturstr, mixr ani adital he tache mukhel tal astat. Rongmachoyeche ujve votten him sogllim vadeam ani vadok astat. Lok bostat tea asnankoddlean poilim mridongovadok, uprant ghottom' vady aslear tem vazoupi tache dave votten fattlean, tache uprant mukhel gaik nott'ttuvonar ho 'tallom'' vazoit purai proyogachim sutram samballotta, tache fattlean ujve votten 'morsing' namvachem vady dant-ontthanche modim dhorun usvasachea adaran tonddan dazoupi vadok asta. Nott'ttuvonara fattlean dave votten tomboro vazoupi asta. Nott'ttuvonarachea fattlean sohaiyok gaik va gayika bosta. Uprant vinna va vayolin vazoupi vadok asta. Vennuvadok aslear to donuy gaikanchea fattlean asta. Bhortonattyomant dakxinnaty songit pod'dot vaprotat.

Bhortonattyomantole bhavo he obhinoyan uktaitat. Angik, vachik, sat'tvik ani ahary oxe obhinoyache char prokar asat. Toxench bhortonattyomant mukheloponnan tin provah ekttham-i zaleat. 1) nottuva melleachem sodir natty. Deudasinche nrity mhonnttat te hench. 2) tonzaurchea bhagout somprodayak onnsorun kortat tem bhagoutomella hem nrityoprodhan natty ani 3) kurvonji namvachem gamvgirem natty. Hea tinuy provahanchem susomvadi mixronn mhollearuch bhortonattyom' oxem xastrache zannkar mhonnttat.

Minakxisundorom' pill'lloi, mut'tukomar pill'lloi, choklingom' pill'lloi, chondroxekhor rill'lloi, ramyea pill'lloi, kitt'ttpa pill'lloi he bhortonattyomantole namneche poromporagot nrityoguru. Gouri om'mall, balasorsvoti, rukminnidevi aeronddel, kolanidhi narainn, mrinnalini sarabhai heo namnecheo nortoki ani ramgopan ho namnecho nortok.

Yamini krixnnomurti ani podma subrohyomyom' heo halincheo namnecheo nortoki. Toxench komla, indranni rehman, sonol mansing, voijyontimala, hema malini heo namnecheo nortoki. Mumboicho nrityoguru parvotikumar hannem tonzaurchea moratthi razamni bhortonattyomakhatir boroil'lea moratthi rochnancher sonxodhon kelem. Tachich xixea ani namnecho moharaxttri-i nortoki sucheta bhidde chapekor himnnem sonxodhon fuddem chalu dourolam.

He kolechi udrogot korpapasot kaim kolasomstha vaur kortat. Bhortonattyomachem pod'dotoxir podvixikxonn divpi 'kolakxetr' hi namnechi somstha chen'nint asa. Egmor hangache 'inddiyon insttittyutt ef fain arttos' he somsthechoi ul'lekh korpak zai. Boddodechea videapittha bhaxenuch halinchea kallant mumboi videapitthanuy bhortonattyom' nachak uchch ani otyuchch podvekhatir mukhel vixoi mhonnun manyota dilea.




